{"ID":270303, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"303\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs302.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs304.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 303<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">extermination of thousands of her citizens to go unpunished, thereby perpetrating a foul and\n  corroding blot upon the fair fame of this great republic, the very thought of which would have\n  caused the high-minded and patriotic framers of the Constitution of the United States to hide their\n  faces with shame.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> Judge, you will aspire to the presidency of the United States; and if ever you turn\n  your hand against me<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> or the Latter-day Saints, you will feel the weight of the hand of the Almighty<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span>\n  upon you; and you will live to see and know that I have testified the truth to you; for the\n  conversation of this day will stick to you through life.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">He [Judge Douglas] appeared very friendly, and acknowledged the truth and propriety of\n  President Smith&rsquo;s remarks. (May 18, 1843.) DHC 5:393-394.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Prophet&rsquo;s Discourse from 2 Peter,<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">First Chapter&mdash;Reproof of Self-Righteousness<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">I do not know when I shall have the privilege of speaking in a house large enough to convene\n  the people. I find my lungs are failing with continual preaching in the open air to large assemblies.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I do not think there have been many good men<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> on the earth since the days of Adam; but there\n  was one good man and his name was Jesus.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> Many persons think a prophet must be a great deal\n  better than anybody else.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> Suppose I would condescend&mdash;yes, I will call it condescend, to be a great\n  deal better than any of you, I would be raised up to the highest heaven; and who should I have to\n  accompany me?<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I love that man better who swears<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> a stream as long as my arm yet deals justice to his neighbors<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span>\n  and mercifully deals his substance to the poor,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> than the long, smooth-faced hypocrite.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I do not want you to think that I am very righteous, for I am not,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> God judges men according\n  to the use they make of the light which He gives them.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">&ldquo;We have a more sure word of prophecy, whereunto you do well to take heed, as unto a light\n  that shineth in a dark place. We were eyewitnesses of his majesty and heard the voice of his\n  excellent glory.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> And what could be more sure? When He was transfigured on the mount,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> what\n  could be more sure to them? Divines have been quarreling for ages about the meaning of this.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116491\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116491)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116491)\">D&amp;C 133:49<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107630\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107630)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107630)\">Amos 1:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114781\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114781)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114781)\">D&amp;C 87:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113570\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113570)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113570)\">D&amp;C 33:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108354\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108354)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108354)\">Mark 10:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108557\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108557)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108557)\">Luke 18:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109066\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109066)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109066)\">Acts 10:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109062\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109062)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109062)\">Acts 10:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111496\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111496)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111496)\">Mosiah 2:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111754\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111754)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111754)\">Alma 1:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112241\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112241)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112241)\">Alma 38:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107843\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107843)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107843)\">Matt. 5:34-37<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108269\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108269)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108269)\">Matt. 26:74<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112302\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112302)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112302)\">Alma 41:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106941\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106941)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106941)\">Prov. 14:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111374\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111374)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111374)\">Jacob 2:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111569\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111569)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111569)\">Mosiah 4:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111767\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111767)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111767)\">Alma 4:12-13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113747\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113747)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113747)\">D&amp;C 42:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115341\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115341)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115341)\">D&amp;C 105:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107860\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107860)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107860)\">Matt. 6:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109102\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109102)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109102)\">Acts 14:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109285\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109285)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109285)\">Rom. 7:23-24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111128\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111128)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111128)\">2 Ne. 4:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111501\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111501)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111501)\">Mosiah 2:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116624\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116624)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116624)\">D&amp;C 137:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110526\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110526)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110526)\">2 Pet. 1:16-19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116294\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116294)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116294)\">D&amp;C 131:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108089\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108089)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108089)\">Matt. 17:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}